- content_for(:title, 'The Theory')
%p
  Every BipolarType is made up of four non-overlapping subtypes. Each subtype is made up of three aspects. Thus every BipolarType will have each of the following twelve aspects.
%h2 The Four Realms
%ul
  -Realm.all.each do |realm|
    %li
      =link_to realm.description, theory_path(realm.letter)
      =surround "(", ")" do
        =realm.mbti
